Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.78,0:25:51.49,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,320)\fad(100,100)}是被關起來了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.55,0:25:52.02,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}希望能再見到你
