Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.53,0:25:54.14,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,350)\fad(100,100)}告訴你一種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.15,0:25:54.53,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,350)\fad(100,100)}奏沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.68,0:25:54.84,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,320)\fad(100,100)}ANGEL  PLAYER…
