Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.71,0:27:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家這麼晚還在外面遊蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.02,0:27:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  必須得懲罰一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.46,0:27:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.10,0:27:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.89,0:28:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.23,0:28:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使不是已經不會傷害我們了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.64,0:28:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.95,0:28:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏是不會對毫無抵抗的我們進行攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.07,0:28:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.98,0:28:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  我們要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.96,0:28:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  以半圓形圍住她
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.06,0:28:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行集中攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.54,0:28:28.19,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是你這傢伙在發號施令
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.34,0:28:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被distortion擋開  也不要停下攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.72,0:28:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.88,0:28:29.50,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.65,0:28:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.06,0:28:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快閃開  由理
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.91,0:28:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.78,0:28:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.09,0:28:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.55,0:28:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼深的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.51,0:28:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.90,0:29:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是致命傷也會很快好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.06,0:29:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的傢伙居然有兩個  到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.26,0:29:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界什麼時候變得這麼莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.43,0:29:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是有緣由的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.71,0:29:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.89,0:29:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得天使領域入侵作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.90,0:29:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.05,0:29:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她的電腦裡不是有一個開發技能的軟件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.96,0:29:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡面有幾個從未見過的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.46,0:29:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是其中一個叫「harmonics」的技能發動了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.77,0:29:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.53,0:29:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個什麼樣的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.12,0:29:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當時沒看畫面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.26,0:29:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是把一個身體分成兩個的技能
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.76,0:29:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.27,0:29:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.36,0:29:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說這也是天使自己用軟件開發的技能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.30,0:29:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但感覺上並非完全相同的兩個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.64,0:29:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這傢伙不同  很好戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.80,0:29:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.50,0:29:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏她只使用保護自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.79,0:29:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用刀刃時也一樣  只是為了擋住子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.07,0:30:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你們這群廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.11,0:30:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.12,0:30:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為笨蛋基本都聚集在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.84,0:30:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我告訴你們其中一個可能性好了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.51,0:30:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假設那個分身的產生
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.14,0:30:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在擁有強烈的攻擊意志的時候的話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.39,0:30:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.16,0:30:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.61,0:30:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說分身一直遵從著當時本體的命令嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.90,0:30:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  奏不可能擁有強烈的攻擊意志
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.46,0:30:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這無所謂  不過你好像很護著她嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.50,0:30:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為  她很可憐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.17,0:30:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.35,0:30:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  現在的問題是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.01,0:30:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和天使的分身戰鬥的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.51,0:30:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是消除方法
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.12,0:30:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.45,0:30:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果分身是因為她的意志而產生的話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.15,0:30:50.82,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙在幹什麼  快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.61,0:30:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也應該能用她的意志來消除吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.63,0:30:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只需要等她醒來不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.25,0:30:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  如果能用意志消除的話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.70,0:31:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她還會躺在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.14,0:31:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是無意識下的產物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.82,0:31:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以連她也無法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.30,0:31:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算同歸於盡也只好拚命上了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.03,0:31:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.81,0:31:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不會消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.44,0:31:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈不是要一直在這個世界存在下去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.91,0:31:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在放過了我們  但明天開始應該不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.19,0:31:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦偏離規範行為  恐怕會立刻和昨天一樣變成一場血戰
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.65,0:31:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不是學生會長？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.61,0:31:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  因為她完全繼承了約束我們的那份意志
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.77,0:31:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上生性好戰  糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.16,0:31:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想反抗也沒有時間去準備
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.13,0:31:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.16,0:31:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些時間要怎樣去爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.47,0:31:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上課  並裝作聽課的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.13,0:31:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能去聽老師講課的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.46,0:31:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真上課的話就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.66,0:31:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不被分身發現的情況下幹別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.38,0:32:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且堅持一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.62,0:32:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望下次再見的時候  不要少了任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.75,0:33:04.80,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,500)\pos(575,250)}女生宿舍  天使領域
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.76,0:33:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我知道可以分身啦
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.84,0:33:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒辦法讓另一個消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.06,0:33:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel  player？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.20,0:33:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟件的使用手冊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.42,0:33:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  這麼厚的書還全是英語
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.85,0:33:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就沒什麼時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.77,0:33:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.93,0:33:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  跳高了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.98,0:33:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是距離嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.75,0:33:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.21,0:33:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.14,0:33:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.51,0:33:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來是連上這個指令就會自動消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.63,0:33:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那它的發動條件是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.55,0:33:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.37,0:33:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆把整個電腦都破壞掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.34,0:33:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡嗎  那分身就不會消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.55,0:34:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  直接改寫成我能明白的程序算了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.02,0:34:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.56,0:34:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間限制是10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.36,0:34:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.58,0:34:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10秒鐘要等起來還真是漫長
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.48,0:34:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不能設置到10秒以下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.51,0:34:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.61,0:34:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.77,0:34:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.28,0:34:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.48,0:34:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.94,0:34:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是分身做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.30,0:34:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要刪除掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.90,0:34:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了  都做得這麼周密了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.59,0:34:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須盡可能少修改一點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.64,0:34:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.09,0:34:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要她再使用一次「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.34,0:34:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「absorb」這個技能就會發動
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.34,0:34:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.75,0:34:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.80,0:34:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己出去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.60,0:35:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.64,0:35:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏和我約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.45,0:35:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會和我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.38,0:35:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做過那種約定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.83,0:35:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.69,0:35:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這副凌亂的樣子肯定是被綁走了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.21,0:35:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.36,0:35:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.83,0:35:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改寫了程序
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.74,0:35:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她再使用一次那個力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.95,0:35:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追加能力就會發動  分身就應該會回到本體
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.24,0:35:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事也能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.25,0:35:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨陣磨槍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.21,0:35:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是敵人的行動比預想的還快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.30,0:35:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被藏起來的話就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.63,0:35:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.85,0:35:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.68,0:35:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要一邊躲避兇惡的天使嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.85,0:35:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是假裝上課就已經夠麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.39,0:35:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻到底能撐多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.51,0:35:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佯攻是說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.38,0:35:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是為了什麼加入GDM的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.70,0:35:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為崇拜巖澤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.69,0:35:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GDM可是為了佯攻而存在的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.00,0:35:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  面對那麼可怕的對手怎麼佯攻呀
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.32,0:35:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你佯攻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.68,0:36:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.46,0:36:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡我可是你的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.60,0:36:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼反倒是你發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.93,0:36:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩嗎  真是對不起了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.81,0:36:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  雖然在演唱會中可能會尿褲子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.02,0:36:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不會退縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.97,0:36:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份決心先謝謝你了  不過現在還不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.75,0:36:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先去做力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.29,0:36:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.67,0:36:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集目擊到天使的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.13,0:36:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey  yo！  Check  this  out！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.95,0:36:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  a  woah  woah  …  headspin
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.99,0:36:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛收集來的情報看
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.96,0:36:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚禁的場所很有可能是在Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.26,0:36:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  一定是在那最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.49,0:36:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個爆破掉的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.52,0:36:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  陷阱也還開啟著
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.56,0:36:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最為危險  距離這裡最遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.85,0:36:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要潛入這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.06,0:36:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次可幾乎是全滅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.22,0:36:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.86,0:36:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一個死的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.13,0:36:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家我即使尿褲子也會繼續唱下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.49,0:36:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現出自己的毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.91,0:36:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對那種對手  佯攻也是等著被秒殺
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.01,0:37:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不需要佯攻  堂堂正正地去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.59,0:37:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要兼顧和天使的戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.63,0:37:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.82,0:37:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.74,0:37:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰內容是空降至Guild
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.35,0:37:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其最底層平安奪回天使的本體
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.66,0:37:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.89,0:37:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的陷阱擱著沒人管  真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.90,0:37:32.35,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B4
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…在這裡碰上天使的話
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.45,0:37:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是會尿褲子的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.21,0:37:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.74,0:37:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.98,0:37:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.89,0:37:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有所謂啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.46,0:37:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.46,0:37:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.70,0:37:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.10,0:37:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有手槍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.73,0:37:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.62,0:37:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「distortion」
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.12,0:38:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.15,0:38:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會比預想的更快搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.45,0:38:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.23,0:38:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.46,0:38:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.54,0:38:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.28,0:38:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙也是分身
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.59,0:38:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.03,0:38:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是敵人又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.96,0:38:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣  那傢伙又是第一個被幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.12,0:38:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.36,0:38:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後的要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.88,0:38:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想這個的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.48,0:38:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先對付眼前的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.39,0:38:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎很忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.52,0:38:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游離子  快沒有子彈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.25,0:38:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去封住路口  跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.27,0:38:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.97,0:38:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由理
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.31,0:39:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.71,0:39:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能趕上的人就留下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.07,0:39:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.03,0:39:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.04,0:39:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.01,0:39:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.07,0:39:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.09,0:39:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.11,0:39:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.18,0:39:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.24,0:39:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.13,0:39:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.22,0:39:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.03,0:39:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼凶暴的天使居然有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.98,0:39:22.76,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B5
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.01,0:39:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比上次空降作戰的處境還要糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.15,0:39:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會出現第二個
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.06,0:39:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身都使用「handsonic」和「distortion」了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.37,0:39:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說「harmonics」也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.62,0:39:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是一群低能兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.32,0:39:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學除外
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.80,0:39:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來總結問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.39,0:39:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有請
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.12,0:39:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題有兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.09,0:39:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是究竟製造了多少個分身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.20,0:39:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然分身能製造分身的話
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.48,0:39:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那數量就沒有限制了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.14,0:39:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那別說是兩個了…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.13,0:39:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十個…二十個  說不定還有更多
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.36,0:39:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.60,0:40:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由理已經追加過技能了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.19,0:40:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身是會回到本體的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.48,0:40:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要等她們消失不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是第二個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.61,0:40:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那能力追加以前
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.82,0:40:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身就已經量產了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.15,0:40:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚民們  終於注意到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.22,0:40:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  音無同學是高貴的貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.77,0:40:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.08,0:40:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她知道我們會潛入這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.20,0:40:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把已經量產了的分身佈置在這個Guild的話
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.74,0:40:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.98,0:40:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,trap
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.42,0:40:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  這是陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.35,0:40:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背後已經有兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.41,0:40:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們不會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.01,0:40:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.26,0:40:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這前方…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.04,0:40:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聚集了很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.30,0:40:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說被困在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.27,0:40:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連武器也沒法補給
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.89,0:40:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是等著被幹掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.96,0:40:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出這種事到底有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.83,0:41:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就結果而言是讓我們完全服從吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.77,0:41:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.99,0:41:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們老老實實地消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.23,0:41:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個把我們一網打盡的絕妙作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.37,0:41:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.85,0:41:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.98,0:41:29.42,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B10
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.22,0:41:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.93,0:41:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再…浪費子彈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.32,0:41:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.48,0:41:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.45,0:41:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  趁我還有意識的時候快走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.38,0:41:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這種好像只有在臨死時才是條好漢的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.40,0:41:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  趁現在快走
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.99,0:41:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐住啊  松下五段
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.11,0:41:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.01,0:41:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.57,0:42:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓松下君白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.34,0:42:07.76,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B11
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.54,0:42:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托他的福我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.42,0:42:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要前進那是最好的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.80,0:42:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天使身體很小
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.58,0:42:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要封住她的動作的話  那樣做是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.13,0:42:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管天使有多麼大的力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.04,0:42:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用柔道的扣體術的話會對她有用
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.87,0:42:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松下君教我們的柔道終於有實用的一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.47,0:42:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說對一個天使只要犧牲一個人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.88,0:42:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.28,0:42:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲就行了？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.16,0:42:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只要我們能救出本體  他們也都能獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.64,0:42:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.24,0:42:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四個
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.37,0:42:39.88,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B12
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.69,0:42:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  my  turn
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.87,0:42:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get  chance  and  luck！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.49,0:42:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.09,0:42:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什麼啊  這種像少年漫畫臨近最終回一樣的劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.27,0:42:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了  繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.51,0:42:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.04,0:43:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現這身肌肉的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.72,0:43:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高松
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.49,0:43:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.95,0:43:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐卷
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.86,0:43:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.79,0:43:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是膚淺
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.96,0:43:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.02,0:43:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  意識到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.24,0:43:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是一名小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.03,0:43:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  在那片黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.49,0:43:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個神情很寂寞的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.62,0:43:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.78,0:43:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來讓你露出笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.26,0:43:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大山
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.78,0:43:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是壞透了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.21,0:43:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無同學  不是的  請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.61,0:43:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是善意的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.70,0:43:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個由我去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.03,0:43:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  誰來說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.31,0:43:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我連他名字都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.41,0:43:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.93,0:44:03.37,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild聯絡通道  B15
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.15,0:44:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第幾個了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.63,0:44:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  早就沒在數了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.36,0:44:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我上
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.84,0:44:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  輪到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.12,0:44:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.88,0:44:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.71,0:44:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.98,0:44:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.06,0:44:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你要前進
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.60,0:44:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.37,0:44:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.78,0:44:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去的話就給我快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.54,0:44:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.67,0:44:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是喜歡他還是討厭他
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.65,0:44:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.32,0:44:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guild被爆破後的遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.75,0:44:38.67,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(575,250)}Guild最底層  爆炸中心
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.28,0:44:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡能一口氣下到最底層
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.34,0:44:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無君和由依去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.69,0:44:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一找到  就催促她使用「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.41,0:44:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.97,0:44:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向君不是也說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.31,0:44:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她等著的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.39,0:44:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.15,0:44:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了  根本不值得一提
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.64,0:44:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請提一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.64,0:44:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.09,0:44:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.32,0:45:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這如果是最後一個作戰就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.67,0:45:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.77,0:45:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.24,0:45:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  由依呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.58,0:45:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎只聽到一聲很短暫的悲鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.17,0:45:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了天使的犧牲品了嗎  太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.25,0:45:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是馬上就來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.91,0:45:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次活下來的又只有我們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.39,0:45:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.04,0:45:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.94,0:45:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該是最後一個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.79,0:45:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.87,0:45:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你別在這裡發呆了  快點去找本體
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.16,0:45:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.86,0:45:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.85,0:46:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.17,0:46:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摀住耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.67,0:46:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.06,0:46:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「howling」
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.24,0:46:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.89,0:46:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.82,0:46:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有暈過去
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.16,0:46:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.25,0:46:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我塞著耳塞聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.27,0:46:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你就死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.87,0:46:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  就用另一把匕首割破你的喉嚨
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.32,0:47:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.45,0:47:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.76,0:47:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.95,0:47:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.62,0:47:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.52,0:47:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰線的大家都拼上了性命來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.75,0:47:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.13,0:47:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.94,0:47:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點勉強你很不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.38,0:47:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是希望你能使用一個能力
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.78,0:47:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.27,0:47:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你用了大家就能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.69,0:47:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.79,0:47:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體能受得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.70,0:47:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  只用一次的話
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.40,0:47:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard  Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.82,0:47:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「harmonics」
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.83,0:47:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像改寫了程序啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.24,0:47:49.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  所有的分身都會回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.69,0:47:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼多冷酷的我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.07,0:47:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.85,0:47:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是分身也有意識
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.13,0:47:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是消失
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.22,0:48:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是同化
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.82,0:48:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊你們的眾多的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.68,0:48:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到她的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.89,0:48:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次性吸收這麼多的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.18,0:48:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得會沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.35,0:48:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.67,0:48:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.78,0:48:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.64,0:48:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.76,0:48:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏






